for _ in range(int(input())):
    n = int(input())
    num_list = list(map(int, input().split()))
    val = -99999
    count = -99999
    for i in set(num_list):
        temp = num_list.count(i)
        if temp > count:

            val = i
        elif temp == count and i < val:
            count = temp
            val = i
    print(val, count)

t = int(input())
for dummy in range(t):
    n = int(input())

    a.append(10001)
    best_v = a[0]
    curr_c = 1
    best_c = 0
    for i in range(1, len(a)):
        if a[i] == a[i - 1]:
            curr_c += 1
